    - "Tier-1 internal leaf" / "Tier-2 edge" / "Tier-3 integration" — for
      tiered service systems
    - "frontend leaf" — Nuxt/React/etc. consuming HTTP APIs
    - "docs leaf" — docs-only, no source code
    - "standalone" — SaaS-plane service parallel to application trunk
      (e.g., wellmed-hq)
    - "stub" — placeholder with no implementation yet
    - "marketing site" / other — anything outside the application graph

